The service was alright. But the store is very nice. According to the staff, the store design is called gallery concept. And apparently only total 30 stores in the entire world have this concept. And sg is one of them.
A delightful assortment of reasonably priced jewellery trinkets and ornaments.

My experience at this outlet was exceptional! Esther, the sales staff, made my visit memorable with her warm demeanor and exceptional assistance. She welcomed me with a smile and was incredibly helpful in every aspect of my purchase. Kudos to Esther for her outstanding customer service!

Experienced great customer service at this outlet. I had bought a pair of dangling earrings the previous day but the big crystal unfortunately dropped and I couldnt find it. The staff here was so kind to provide and one-for-one replacement. Thank you.
